> Hello. My name is Benson and I'm with Opto 22 in Temecula, California, USA. My background is in IT since the 80s, and in IA for the last 28 years. I'm eager to learn and share all things IoT, IIoT, I4.0, Digital Transformation, and more. Huge fan and supporter of community driven outlets like this and of @zackscriven and @Walker Reynolds work in this space. Presented a TEDx Talk back in 2014 on IoT from a personal perspective: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_AlcRoqS65E&t
> Thanks for reading! -Benson
@Benson Hougland This is an excellent talk. Benson does a great job at connecting the Internet of Things in a consumer world to our industrial world & IIoT

